dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Pope County, Minnesota, C-15, Part A, Plate 2, Bedrock Geology, Bedrock Topography, and Depth to Bedrock
dc_description_s: Maps showing interpretations of bedrock geology (distribution of rock at the land surface and beneath surface sediments), elevation of the bedrock surface (bedrock topography) and thickness of unconsolidated (glacial and stream sediments) material over the bedrock surface, scale 1:200,000, Pope County.
